description:
Change the way you explore. Trimble Outdoors Navigator is a free GPS navigation and mapping app for all your outdoor and backcountry adventures.

This app is BEST FOR: GPS route finding; map and compass navigation; topo maps; recording trips like hiking, camping, paddling, backcountry skiing, ATV riding, offroading, snowshoeing

Watch Video: http://youtu.be/Q95tBOh8EDQ
------
** START WITH GREAT MAPS **

• View five different map types: streets, hybrid, aerial, topo and terrain. 
• Get exclusive and enhanced topo maps from MyTopo. Access more than 68,000 topo maps in US and Canada that are seamlessly stitched together for fast and easy viewing. Topos scales are 1:24K in the Lower 48, 1:63K in Alaska and 1:50K in Canada.
• Upgrade to the PRO app. Trimble Outdoors Navigator Pro lets you save four different map types on your iPhone, so you can view maps in remote locations without a data or Wifi connection.

** POWERFUL NAVIGATION TOOLS ** 
Digital Compass: Navigate with a digital compass. Choose between: Magnetic North and True North. 

Waypoints: Mark waypoints like trailheads, summits, important turns, and campsites on to the map. Add names and detailed descriptions. Go to previous marked waypoints too. 

Tracks: Track your route on the map. 

Goto: Use the Goto feature to navigate from your current location to a waypoint. 

Guide Trips: Use trips previously recorded by you or others to help guide you on the trail, on remote backroads, and more.

** CHRONICLE YOUR ADVENTURE ** 
Capture Media: Take geo-tagged photos and audio clips of your trip. 
Stat Tracking: See 10+ adventure stats, such as distance, speed, elevation and more 

Share with Friends: Share your adventure on Facebook and TrimbleOutdoors.com 

Trips: Access to thousands trips around the U.S. and Canada

** SAVE TO THE TRIP CLOUD ** 
Register a free account to save your outdoor trips to our Trip Cloud. Benefits include:

• Store and backup unlimited trips. Never lose files again. 

• Auto-sync trips between your computer, iPhone and tablet device. 

• Enhance trips from Trimble Outdoors Navigator with map tools at trimbleoutdoors.com, including .gpx import, geo-tagged photos and videos, turn-by-turn routes and more (Elite or Trip Planner membership required). 

• Open trips in our tablet trip-planning app, Trimble Outdoors MyTopo Maps. 

• Share and exchange trips with the Trimble Outdoors community or privately between outdoor friends.

** LEARN MORE ** 
Visit our website and check out thousands of trips submitted by the Trimble Outdoors community. Click over to: trimbleoutdoors.com.

Feedback Wanted: Found a bug? Want a new feature? Drop us a line on our Facebook page, facebook.com/trimbleoutdoors.

Note: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
releaseNotes:
• USNG support added
• Charts screen added to Stats screen.
• Ability to delete Mega Offline Maps within the app.
• Offline Maps added to the Jump menu for fast switching.
• Fixed a crash that was causing iOS 5 to crash when entering to any screen.
• Fixed an issue that was preventing Private Lands not to show up for some counties.
• Fixed an issue that was preventing pro trips to download correctly.
• Fix an issue that was causing total distance to not update when downloading new tracks from the website.
